    "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"id\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Daftar Penipu | CuanGaming</title>\n<style>\nbody{margin:0;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;background:#0f172a;color:#e5e7eb;padding:16px}\nh1{font-size:22px}\np{font-size:14px;color:#cbd5f5}\n.search-box{margin:16px 0}\n.search-box input{width:100%;padding:12px;border-radius:8px;border:none;font-size:14px}\n.table-wrapper{overflow-x:auto}\ntable{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;background:#020617;min-width:700px}\nth,td{padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #1e293b;font-size:13px;text-align:left}\nth{color:#38bdf8}\ntr:hover{background:#020617cc;cursor:pointer}\n.badge{padding:4px 8px;border-radius:6px;font-size:11px}\n.verified{background:#16a34a;color:#fff}\n.modal{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.85);justify-content:center;align-items:center;padding:16px}\n.modal-content{background:#020617;padding:16px;border-radius:10px;max-width:600px;width:100%;max-height:90vh;overflow:auto}\n.close{float:right;color:#f87171;cursor:pointer;font-size:18px}\nimg{max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin-top:10px}\n@media(max-width:768px){h1{font-size:18px}table{min-width:100%}th,td{font-size:12px;padding:8px}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h1>ðŸš¨ Daftar Penipu</h1>\n<p>Cek nomor HP, rekening, atau akun sebelum transaksi.</p>\n<div class=\"search-box\">\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"searchInput\" placeholder=\"Cari nomor HP, rekening, atau akun...\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>No</th>\n<th>Nomor HP</th>\n<th>Rekening / E-Wallet</th>\n<th>Nama Akun</th>\n<th>Nama Rekening</th>\n<th>Status</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody id=\"penipuList\">\n<tr onclick=\"openModal()\">\n<td>1</td>\n<td>08123456789</td>\n<td>BCA 123456789</td>\n<td>@penipu_judi</td>\n<td>ANDI</td>\n<td><span class=\"badge verified\">VERIFIED</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal\" id=\"detailModal\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<span class=\"close\" onclick=\"closeModal()\">âœ–</span>\n<h3>Detail Laporan Penipuan</h3>\n<p><b>Nomor HP:</b> 08123456789</p>\n<p><b>Rekening:</b> BCA 123456789</p>\n<p><b>Nama Akun:</b> @penipu_judi</p>\n<p><b>Nama Rekening:</b> ANDI</p>\n<p><b>Kronologi:</b><br>Pelaku menawarkan akun VIP, setelah transfer langsung memblokir korban.</p>\n<img src=\"bukti.jpg\" alt=\"Bukti Penipuan\">\n</div>\n</div>\n<script>\ndocument.getElementById('searchInput').addEventListener('keyup',function(){let f=this.value.toLowerCase();document.querySelectorAll('#penipuList tr').forEach(r=>{r.style.display=r.innerText.toLowerCase().includes(f)?'':'none'})});\nfunction openModal(){document.getElementById('detailModal').style.display='flex'}\nfunction closeModal(){document.getElementById('detailModal').style.display='none'}\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
